author: wddgit
body:
#### PR description:

This is part of a Core campaign to eliminate all references to legacy type modules from CMSSW. This gets rid of the last such module under L1.

TestBxOrConfig is deleted because it is a legacy version of the test module DumpL1RPCBxOrConfig, which is already a ```global``` type module and does everything it can do and more. It's also already not compiled and compilation has been broken since at least January 2023.

I also deleted a test configuration that does nothing more than run the deleted module. And I also deleted some unnecessary includes that were already commented out (one of which included the legacy header).

#### PR validation:

None. Just deletions of unused code.
title: Delete last L1 legacy type module
